        </p>
        <div class="buttons">
          <ButtonPrimary content="Add to cart" />
          <ButtonSecondary content="Learn more" />
        </div>
        <!-- <Picture
          class="shot"
          src={card_1}
          alt="Robot"
          fetchpriority={"high"}
          quality={"max"}
        /> -->
      </div>
      <div class="card with-border no-shot">
        <strong class="shade"></strong>
        <strong class="shade"></strong>
        <!-- <h3>Battery</h3> -->
        <span> NVIDIA Jetson Orin NX </span>
        <p>
          Boost the computing power for complex AI models and real-time data
          processing.
        </p>
        <div class="buttons">
          <ButtonPrimary content="Add to cart" />
          <ButtonSecondary content="Learn more" />
        </div>
        <!-- <Picture
          class="shot"
          src={card_2}
          alt="Robot"
          fetchpriority={"high"}
          quality={"max"}
        /> -->
      </div>
      <div class="card with-border no-shot">
        <strong class="shade"></strong>
        <strong class="shade"></strong>
        <!-- <h3>SDK</h3> -->
        <span> Unitree SDK </span>
        <p>
          Access the open-source development kit for full control over motion,
          perception, and custom application creation
        </p>
        <div class="buttons">
          <ButtonPrimary content="Add to cart" />
          <ButtonSecondary content="Learn more" />
        </div>
        <!-- <Picture
          class="shot"
          src={card_3}
          alt="Robot"
          fetchpriority={"high"}
          quality={"max"}
        /> -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="book-section">
    <div class="book-wrapper">
      <div class="first">
        <strong class="shade"></strong>
        <strong class="shade"></strong>
        <h4 class="title">
          Power Your <br class="br-desktop" /> Research with the <br
            class="br-desktop"
          /> H1 Series
        </h4>
        <p class="paragraph-1">
          The Unitree H1 Series is available exclusively through AIROBOTS in
          Greece. Contact us to discuss your academic or industrial research
          needs, request a detailed quote, or schedule a technical consultation.
        </p>
        <div class="buttons">
          <ButtonPrimary
            content="Request a quote"
            type="a"
            href={pages.product.path}
          />
          <ButtonSecondary content="Contact Technical Support" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="second">
        <Picture
          class="book-bck"
          src={book_bck}
          alt=""
          fetchpriority={"high"}
          quality={"max"}
        />
        <Picture
          class="book-shot"
          src={modelShot}
          alt=""
          fetchpriority={"high"}
          quality={"max"}
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

